item.title: Luxura Analysis Part 1
item.description: Situation In this project, I’m part of Luxura’s Data Analytics team. As fashion e-commerce company, Luxura selling several luxury fashion brands. In order to expand business partnership, Luxura needed to decide which brand to prioritize as their main brand partnership based on historical performance. Backround Luxura is an e-commerce company that exclusively sells high-end fashion brands including Adibi, Balena, and Celinna . These brands have seen increasing market share over the past 3 years and rely on Luxura as their sole retail partner.
